# deploy-test ŌĆö AdvertEyes improve pass 3

## API Verification

| Endpoint | Result |
|---|---|
| `api.michaelwegter.com/health` | 200 `{"status":"ok","version":"1.0.0"}` |
| `api.michaelwegter.com/adverteyes/health` | 200 `{"ok":true,"service":"adverteyes-api"}` |
| `POST /adverteyes/auth/login` (admin) | JWT issued, `role: admin` |
| `GET /adverteyes/campaigns` | 8 campaigns returned |
| `GET /adverteyes/inventory` | Units array returned |
| `GET /adverteyes/bookings` | Booking data returned |
| `GET /adverteyes/weather/1` | Live data: keys `unit, current, hourly, timezone, fetched_at` |
| `GET /adverteyes/clients` | 5 clients returned |

Note: `/adverteyes/analytics` route does not exist on the backend ŌĆö the frontend Analytics page derives analytics from `campaigns` + `inventory` + `bookings` calls (confirmed in source). Not a bug.

