## Notes

- `/work-samples/adverteyes` returns HTTP 404 to curl (expected ŌĆö GH Pages SPA 404.html trick). A real browser session correctly renders the iframe demo.
- 401 infinite-reload bug (fixed in prior pass, commit `23881e2`) confirmed resolved: admin login navigates to `/dashboard` cleanly with no loop.
- Analytics endpoint absence on backend is benign ŌĆö page uses existing campaign/inventory/booking endpoints.

